            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have been here for 7 years !! And I'm so proud of myself that I studied in this school!😌❤️\n\nTeachers focus on Value system towards School, Teachers, subject, parents, etc. For report card gradings which is good actually! I haven't seen any other KV school focusing on Value system, they blindly give A grades (or grades according to the teacher's liking the student).\n\nI never understood the value of Value system until I got transferred to another KV where students didn't had manners at all!\n\nThis School is an achiever, participates in various competitions nationwide. It produces students with a competitive nature and a bit urban Kolkata City like attitude.\n\nDo admit your child(ren) if you want all round exposure and development.",
